
(IN relation to __init__.py) will make the website folder a python package (using packaged 
parts of it)

Pip = package install for python
Flask is for python to make website creation easier
- flask-login is to login users
- flask-sqlalchemy data base for sql 

"the reason we can do this is because website is a python package, so whenever you put 
this init.py file inside of a folder it becomes a python package which means when u input 
the name of the folder it will by default run all of the stuff in the init .py file 